about.mainHeading: OVER 25 YEARS, WE ARE YOUR RELIABLE ELECTRICITY COMPANY
about.about: Filsi OÜ is an Estonian electricity company, founded in 1997. We specialize in electrical installations, offering services in external grid construction, internal works, contact network construction, excavation works, substation construction, operations and maintenance, design and planning, and construction works. Filsi OÜ has a large fleet of machinery, and our significant projects include Kakumäe Harbor, Module Tech, Eesti Traat, and Favorit. We are known for providing professional service, delivering reliable electrical works, and ensuring the safety and reliability of electrical systems.

equipmentInfo.equipmentDesc: JCB 4CX is a four-wheel-drive versatile construction machine widely used in excavation, loading, road construction, and many other construction tasks. It ensures excellent performance, precision, and efficiency even on the most demanding construction sites. The JCB 4CX features a four-telescopic boom that allows for extensive and flexible use. Additionally, it is equipped with an advanced control system, making it easy and intuitive to operate.

Yanmar VIO80 is a compact crawler excavator, perfect for construction sites requiring greater digging depth and lifting capacity. It features a powerful engine that ensures high performance and fuel efficiency. The Yanmar VIO80 is equipped with a modern hydraulic system that allows for smooth and precise operation. Additionally, it has a comfortable and spacious operator cabin, providing a pleasant working environment for the operator.

Yanmar VIO23 is a compact excavator that is excellent for smaller construction and digging tasks. It features a compact design, allowing access to narrow spaces. The Yanmar VIO23 has a reliable hydraulic system, enabling smooth operations and precise movements. It also comes with an intuitive control panel, making it user-friendly, even for beginners.

Yanmar SVO8 is a compact crawler excavator that can be easily maneuvered in confined spaces. It is perfect for gardening, landscaping, and smaller construction tasks. The Yanmar SVO8 features strong hydraulic performance, enabling fast and efficient work. Additionally, it has a tilting cabin, allowing easy access for maintenance and repairs.

Bobcat S175 is a compact and powerful skid-steer loader used for material handling and various construction tasks. It has high lifting capacity and a stable construction, ensuring safe and efficient operations. The Bobcat S175 features an ergonomic operator cabin and an intuitive control panel, making it comfortable to use.

Bobcat E16 is a compact excavator perfect for smaller digging tasks. It features a powerful engine, allowing smooth and efficient excavation. The Bobcat E16 has a compact design, enabling access to narrow spaces. Additionally, it is equipped with a modern control system, making it easy to use.

about.heading: RECOGNIZED LEADER IN ELECTRICAL CONSTRUCTION
about.about:
Filsi Ltd. is an Estonian electrical company founded in 1997. The company specializes in electrical assembly works and offers various services. These services include external network construction, interior works, contact network construction, excavation works, substation construction, operation, design, and construction works. Filsi Ltd. has an impressive fleet of construction equipment covering a wide range of machinery.
 The company has carried out several notable projects, including Kakumäe Harbor, Module Tech, Eesti Traat, and Favor. These large projects have helped strengthen Filsi Ltd.'s reputation and experience in the field of electrical assembly.
 Filsi Ltd. is known for its professional and reliable service, and they have an experienced team capable of delivering high-quality results for various electrical projects. The company's goal is to provide customers with the best possible solution to meet their electrical needs and ensure the safety and reliability of electrical systems.
